{"tid":2331883,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★台灣-影視作品上字幕時一定要用繁體中文字，如用簡體 罰款 100 萬台幣","createTime":"2020-12-19T07:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-20T05:23:03.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1148,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"8918c99f895569d45f73a8537dcc1329930bfdb8","tid":2331883,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T07:11:03.000Z","msg":"台灣政府部門國家通訊傳播委員會( NCC ) 近日將研究擬定「網際網路視聽服務管理法」，而其中一條條文規定，網絡平台為影視作品上字幕時，一定要用繁體中文字，如果用簡體中文字就會遭罰款 100 萬台幣，有資深媒體人表示，罰款較重，一些小本經營的網絡平台難以負擔罰款。<br />\n <br />\n台灣民進黨立委范雲曾在「鄉民大會」節目表示，NCC 研究及擬定法例，主要是針對「數位網路視聽」平台，例如 Netflix、愛奇藝，以保障本地影視作品。資深媒體人邱明玉指出，「網際網路視聽服務管理法」當中有一項具爭議的條文，要求網絡平台為影視作品上字幕時，必須用繁體字，如果用簡體字，就會遭罰款 100 萬台幣<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/19/taiwan-ncc-words/life-tech/social-network/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F19%2Ftaiwan-ncc-words%2Flife-tech%2Fsocial-network%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBegAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=653f2c67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/19/taiwan-ncc-words/life-tech/social-network/</a>"},{"pid":"00fc5b92b61a07a5703f5a2f7bec9b224ad83edb","tid":2331883,"uid":19454,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T07:11:15.000Z","msg":"德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"401a98464c6ff7d9023bdf47b0b2d88f9bafae8a","tid":2331883,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T07:11:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj